svg.title: {\displaystyle {\begin{aligned}&\mathrm {Var} [L_{h}|K(x)\geq h]\\&=\sum _{k=h}^{\infty }v^{2(k-h)}\mathrm {Var} [\Lambda _{k}|K(x)\geq h]\\&=\mathrm {Var} [\Lambda _{h}|K(x)\geq h]+v^{2}\mathrm {Var} [L_{h+1}|K(x)\geq h]\\&=\sum _{k=h}^{h+j-1}v^{2(k-h)}\mathrm {Var} [\Lambda _{k}|K(x)\geq h]+v^{2j}\mathrm {Var} [L_{h+j}|K(x)\geq h]\end{aligned}}}
